A happy 2023 to everyone! Hope you guys enjoyed your holidays and celebrations 🎉 I'm ringing in the new year with a print release of my most popular image from 2022 - 'World's a Stage' prints will be for sale this Thursday, January 5th at 1pm PST (4pm EST) through @peoplesprints 🖤 
.
If interested, visit www.thepeoplesprintshop.com - a clickable link is available through the linktree on my profile. I'll be sure to share more leading up to the drop. Thanks! #peoplesprintshop

You can find them through the linktree on my profile or by visiting www.thepeoplesprintshop.com. Biggest thanks to everyone who has purchased! Truly appreciate all your support 🥰✨ #peoplesprintshop

Before 'The Last of Us' aired on HBO, I was commissioned by a collector to tackle two paintings inspired by the video game series. Here's my first painting depicting the game's heroine, Ellie, and her partner Dina 🧡 (second painting will be shared as a separate post) - 'Home', 16x20", oil and acrylic on panel.
.
Though I haven't played a video game in more a decade or so now, I certainly grew up enjoying them and was still aware of the beloved series, nonetheless. It was a pleasure to paint these works, thanks for the opportunity and trust Andrew! ☺️ #thelastofus #ellieanddina

Second commissioned work inspired by the video game series 'The Last of Us' - 'Days of You and I', 14x18", oil on panel. Portrait resemblance is based off the game and not the show's actress (though the show was awesome in its own rite)
.
Made a post previous to this one with the first painting as well. Was a fun subject to paint, even if I haven't played the games myself. Appreciated the opportunity ✨ #thelastofus #elliewilliams

Excited to start sharing WIP's and shots of all the new work I have in store for my next solo show, 'Upon Another Shore', opening at @thinkspace_art July 8th! 
.
Another year of keeping my work underwraps till it's close enough to begin promoting ✨ I'm considering this solo as an extension/continuation from the mini solo I held at Thinskpace last fall - playing more with similar aesthetics and themes I wasn't done experimenting with back then.
.
If interested in the show or the future collector's preview, visit www.thinkspaceprojects.com or email contact@thinkspaceprojetcs.com 👍 
.
Will share plenty more over the coming month. Thanks! #thinkspaceprojects #thinkspacefamily #wip #uponanothershore

“Slight of Hand" was one of the most requested works featured in Sarah Joncas’s recent mini solo exhibition 'Washed Ashore’ that took place with us at the end of last year.

We're excited to now offer “Slight of Hand" as a limited edition giclee print that will be available this Friday in celebration of her new solo show 'Upon Another Shore' that opens on July 8. The team over at Static Medium have done an incredible job recreating this beautiful work on wood panel from Sarah Joncas. The finished print simply glows with energy.

@sarah_joncas
"Slight of Hand"
Fine art print on Moab Entrada 290gsm paper
Hand deckled edges
16 x 20 inches / 40.6 x 50.8 cm
Edition of 40
Hand signed and numbered by the artist

Available this Friday, July 7 at 10am PST / 1pm EST via our web shop (link in bio). Please be sure to use Google to check the exact time in your area.

Shipping costs are additional and will be calculated during check out. Any customs or duty fees incurred, are not the responsibility of the gallery.
�
Sorry, no pre-sales of any kind are available. Thank you.

#sarahjoncas #thinkspacegallery #limitededition #artprint

'Darkest Light', 18x24", oil and acrylic on panel
.
Another piece with a more abstracted background choice... A lot of these choices I made with this recent body of work were inspired by the 'errors' and rough work I did through Photoshop creating my compositions. often using a mouse to draw in colours or haphazardly cutting and pasting, I began to embrace them rather than correct them 😉
.
View the whole show online through the linktree on my profile! Currently on view at @thinkspace_art until July 29th - www.thinkspaceprojects.com #thinkspacefamily #thinkspaceprojects #uponanothershore
